item.description:
This is easily the best podcast episode I’ve heard this year..

Genuine, kind, authentic. Absolutely incredible storytelling.

I aspire to have the range of stories that @JaredBWeinstein shared on the pod. 

@jacksondahl &amp;amp; @DialecticPod always crush but this was special 👏

